@dabbinavo 
The Zscaler issue can likely be resolved by exporting the Zscaler certificate from the certificate store and setting it in the environment variable `NODE_EXTRA_CA_CERTS`.
The built-in Node.js in VS Code uses its own certificate, causing it to recognize the certificate replaced by Zscaler as invalid.

